      "text": "<b>Therefore</b>, create an official way for participants to communicate to you anonymously. Important information might be communicated to you via this path that would otherwise not reach you at all. If the group works well, <i>[[PERSONAL COMMUNICATION]]</i> will suffice to solve problems. If this pattern gets used heavily, this indicates that there are serious problems within the group or in the relationship participants/teacher.\n  ",
