      "text": "An example for this pattern might be a real mailbox somewhere in the class room where participants can put notes. Email and web technology offers other possibilities, of course. At the end of the seminar, offer feedback forms that can be filled by the participants anonymously. Of course, if the groups works well, <i>[[PERSONAL COMMUNICATION]]</i> can help to avoid problems that make this pattern necessary.\n  ",
